00:24:57.880 --> 00:25:01.370 align:middle line:84%
to participate and be
interactive instead of just one

00:25:01.370 --> 00:25:02.310 align:middle line:90%
way, taught at.

00:25:02.310 --> 00:25:03.310 align:middle line:90%
>>BOULTER: That's right.

00:25:03.310 --> 00:25:06.300 align:middle line:84%
And, see, language learning
