00:25:10.710 --> 00:25:12.185 align:middle line:90%
But you can't order lunch.

00:25:12.185 --> 00:25:13.490 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: There you go.

00:25:13.490 --> 00:25:14.906 align:middle line:84%
>>BOULTER: And
