it's all appealing

00:25:21.517 --> 00:25:22.850 align:middle line:90%
to different parts of the brain.

00:25:22.850 --> 00:25:26.020 align:middle line:84%
But it's not necessarily
appealing to the whole person.

00:25:26.020 --> 00:25:27.780 align:middle line:90%
Interactivity is the key.

00:25:27.780 --> 00:25:29.450 align:middle line:90%
And immediacy of feedback.

00:25:29.450 --> 00:25:32.570 align:middle line:84%
So if you do an exercise and you
get the answers a week later,

00:25:32.570 --> 00:25:34.205 align:middle line:84%
you don't remember
that exercise.

00:25:34.205 --> 00:25:35.220 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: No,
you're already gone.

00:25:35.220 --> 00:25:36.050 align:middle line:90%
It's like training a dog.

00:25:36.050 --> 00:25:36.842 align:middle line:90%
You're out of that.

00:25:36.842 --> 00:25:37.549 align:middle line:90%
>>BOULTER: Right.

00:25:37.549 --> 00:25:38.490 align:middle line:90%
You forget about it.

00:25:38.490 --> 00:25:39.240 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:41.370 align:middle line:84%
>>BOULTER: So if, as
