and you got 75%,

00:25:58.070 --> 00:25:59.980 align:middle line:84%
you get taken back
into the lesson.

00:25:59.980 --> 00:26:00.480 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And that's good.

00:26:00.480 --> 00:26:00.820 align:middle line:90%
That's fair enough.

00:26:00.820 --> 00:26:03.020 align:middle line:84%
>>BOULTER: And then you
keep going around and around

00:26:03.020 --> 00:26:03.610 align:middle line:90%
until you can get 100%.

00:26:03.610 --> 00:26:05.000 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And it's private.

